    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em> You seize opportunity as it comes, taking advantage of your enemy's poor position after a missed attack.</em></p><p><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Scarlet Throne Style, Scarlet Throne Dignity, Sense Motive 11 Ranks.</p><p><strong>Benefit</strong>: Whenever you use an ability to negate an attack from an opponent (such as with a counter or with the Scarlet Throne Dignity feat), that opponent provokes an attack of opportunity from you. A given creature can only provoke an attack of opportunity from you in this way once per round.</p>",
